        "id": 1000487
      },
      "writtenOn": "2019-06-17T14:06:23Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "That\u0027s a good question. Eventually we need to surface this information to task_runner, which will set the right state in the task. This will have to evolve over time. I\u0027m fine with starting with this at the moment and change it as needed later.",
